    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un mehſ effam tohs kawuſchi / un wiẍxu Senuni uſnehmuſchi / un to par Jhpaſchunu\ndewis teem Rubbeniteereem / un\nteem Gaditeeem / un tai puſs\nZilti Manaſſus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nu turrajt ſchahs Derribas Wahrdus/un darrajt tohs/\nka juhs gndri turrajtees eekſch wiſfa/ ko juhs darriſeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Inhs ſtahwat ſchodeen wiſfi vreeſſco ta KUNGA juhfu Dee wa / juhfu Ziltu Wirfineeki / un\njuhfu Wezzajee/ un juhfu Uſraugi/ wiſſi Iſraêla Wihr.\n"
