    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tu eedohtohs eekſch ta\nKUNGA tawa Deewa Derribas / un eekſch tahs Svehreſchanas / ko tas KUNGS taws\nDeews ſchodeen ar tew darra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka wiꞥſch tew ſchodeen few\npar Eaudim eezeelt / un tew par\nDeewu irr / itt ka wiꞥſch tew\n"
