      "text": "Bet tik labbi ar juhs/\nkas juhs ſchodeen ar mums ſche\nſtahwat vreeſſch ta KUNGA\nmuhſu Deewa / ka ar teem / kas\nſchodeen ſche pee mums ne ſtahw\n"
