    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo juhs finnat / ka mehe\nEgiptes-Semmê effam dſihwojſchi/ un ka mehſ widdu zaur teem\nPagaſteem effam gabjuſchi / kur\njuhs effat zaurgahjuſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un juhs effat redſejſchi win.\nnu Negantivas un Elkus/ Kohku\nnn Akmini/Sudrabu un Seltukas pee teem bija.\n"
